title: Ebro In The Morning - Knicks-Nets Unity + Manhattan DA candidate Tali Farhadian Weinstein
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning this episode aired on 6/3.

On this episode, Manhattan DA candidate Tali Farhadian Weinstein comes onto Ebro in the Morning to discuss her campaign (1:15:00)

Ebro talks to Knicks fans about whether or not they'll unify and support the Nets (45:00) and says that Knicks fans played themselves (16:00), Rosenberg's album comes out tomorrow, and Laura Stylez has her patented Flashing Lights segments (12:30, & 1:08:00).

Please like and subscribe to Ebro In The Morning.
